thread.title: John Y
thread.title_full: Gym Direct reviewed by John Y

author: John Y
title: John Y
text:
Great service and good price.
Taken one star off because the metal J-hooks of the power rack (their most popular one) scratch the knurling on the the barbell. The knurling will be gone in no time and that will make the barbell useless for doing snatches. The J-hooks from the more expensive commercial grade racks will have hard plastic backings.
